OL,6,FA man from Wiltshire who stole tens of
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds from his elderly
OL,8,Fparents has been jailed.
OL,10,FBrett Conway, formerly of Stanton St
OL,11,FQuinton, has been sentenced to six
OL,12,Fyears and eight months in prison.
OL,14,FThe 66-year-old took more than #50,000
OL,15,Ffrom his parents to help fund what
OL,16,Fpolice described as a "lavish
OL,17,Flifestyle" and pay off "substantial
OL,18,Fcredit card debt".
OL,20,F'Cruel and bullying'
