OL,3,CMan who stole tens of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds from elderly parents jailed
OL,6,FBetween December 2017 and June 2018,
OL,7,FConway independently transferred
OL,8,Falmost #52,000 out of the joint
OL,9,Faccount of his father, who was
OL,10,Fsuffering from severe dementia, and
OL,11,Fhis elderly mother.
OL,13,FHe claimed it was for mortgage
OL,14,Fpayments and building work on the
OL,15,Fproperty in which his parents lived,
OL,16,Fwhich Conway owned.
