OL,3,CMan who stole tens of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds from elderly parents jailed
OL,6,FDuring the investigation however, it
OL,7,Fwas established that much of the money
OL,8,Fwas being used to cover Conway's
OL,9,Fcredit card debt of more than #75,000
OL,10,Fand to fund multiple foreign holidays
OL,11,Fa year.
OL,13,FWhen Conway was challenged by his
OL,14,Fmother, he accepted what he had done
OL,15,Fbut refused to reimburse his parents
OL,16,For cooperate with them.
OL,18,FAccording to Wiltshire Police, the
OL,19,Ftrauma of the thefts left his mother
OL,20,Fin a care home, and both his parents
OL,21,Fhave since died.
