OL,4,Cpounds from elderly parents jailed
OL,6,F'Manipulative individual'
OL,8,FFollowing his initial arrest on
OL,9,Fsuspicion of theft, police say Conway
OL,10,Fwaged an "obsessive and escalated
OL,11,Fcampaign" against both his former
OL,12,Fpartner, who had provided a witness
OL,13,Fstatement, and his parents.
OL,15,FHe drafted retraction letters, as well
OL,16,Fas making repeated "ugly, unfounded
OL,17,Faccusations" about his former
OL,18,Fpartner's character which he made
OL,19,Fincreasingly public.
