OL,3,CMan who stole tens of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds from elderly parents jailed
OL,6,FHe also threatened not to cooperate
OL,7,Fwith solicitors in a civil case and
OL,8,Fattempted to weigh them down in legal
OL,9,Ffees.
OL,11,FFollowing an investigation by the
OL,12,FWiltshire Police Complex Fraud Team,
OL,13,Fhe was charged with two counts of
OL,14,Ftheft and one count of perverting the
OL,15,Fcourse of justice.
OL,17,F'Brazen behaviour'
