OL,3,CMan who stole tens of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds from elderly parents jailed
OL,6,FDet Con Rachael Fairbairn of the Fraud
OL,7,Fteam said: "The court heard how
OL,8,FConway's behaviour became increasingly
OL,9,Fcruel and bullying to anyone or any
OL,10,Forganisation that stood in his way,
OL,11,Fmeaning he was exhausting and
OL,12,Fsometimes frightening to deal with.
OL,14,F"That brazen behaviour only made the
OL,15,Fdamage caused to his victims all the
OL,16,Fmore painful. They couldn't quite
OL,17,Fbelieve what was happening and it just
OL,18,Fwent on and on, subjecting his elderly
OL,19,Fand vulnerable family to a seemingly
OL,20,Fendless campaign of bullying.
