OL,3,CMan who stole tens of thousands of
OL,4,Cpounds from elderly parents jailed
OL,6,F"In desperation, they even told him he
OL,7,Fcould keep all the money if he simply
OL,8,Fleft them alone. He didn't and they
OL,9,Frealised a criminal investigation was
OL,10,Fthe only way to stop him.
OL,12,F"It's very sad that the victims have
OL,13,Fdied before the matter was concluded
OL,14,Fat court but I am pleased Conway will
OL,15,Fnow face justice for his actions."
OL,17,FAction is now underway to recover the
OL,18,Fmoney through the Proceeds of Crime
OL,19,FAct.
